          Get Started in Minutes
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Install SigmOS and start building intelligent systems right away
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-gray-900/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-gray-800/50 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 bg-gray-800/50 border-b border-gray-700/50">
            <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-mono">Terminal</span>
            <button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm">Copy</button>
          </div>
          <pre class="p-6 text-left overflow-x-auto"><code class="text-sm font-mono text-gray-300"># Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/copyleftdev/sigmos.git
cd sigmos

# Build the project
cargo build --release

# Install the CLI
cargo install --path crates/cli

# Run your first spec
sigmos run examples/agent.sigmos</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 relative">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
